title: Southampton 1 Norwich City 0: Shane Long pops up with 92nd-minute goal to prove stay-away fans were right to swerve dull FA Cup third-round replay
text:
EFL UNLUCKY 13,517 Southampton 1 Norwich City 0: Shane Long pops up with 92nd-minute goal to prove stay-away fans were right to swerve dull FA Cup third-round replay 
Only 13,517 fans made it to St Mary's and they almost had to sit through 90 minutes plus added time before the faint hope of some exciting penalties was dashed by Long's strike by DAN KING
